	* code/inc/error.inc:
	  removed

2003-01-20 16:55  Matthias Steffens <refbase@extracts.de>

	* code/php/: advanced_search.php, index.php, library_search.php, modify.php,
	  record.php, search.php, simple_search.php, user_details.php,
